rows.label: tlk001201_07_msg0001
rows.name:
To think that they were controlling
Genbu itself...

rows.label: tlk001201_07_msg0002
rows.name:
No more Core Chips were being
produced, so there was no longer
any need to offer anything to Acedia.

rows.label: tlk001201_07_msg0003
rows.name:
Slowly but surely, Genbu was returning
to its former vitality. We were hoping
that our problems were over...

rows.label: tlk001201_07_msg0004
rows.name:
We have been far too lenient on Acedia,
it seems.

rows.label: tlk001201_07_msg0005
rows.name:
And from all this, there is something
else I now understand.

rows.label: tlk001201_07_msg0006
rows.name:
That it is you who have the power to
determine the future of Alst...
